column5: The Dark Bird Palace is the paint studio of the most famous flea market artist in the world, Kelly Moore. The Flea Market shrine is built of odds and ends from the market and old paintings of the artist and stands on the famous (820) Canyon Roadd next to the TeaHouse in Santa Fe, New Mexico.
column6: A famous flea market artist's studio that's full of odds and ends.
column8: 821 Canyon Road; Santa Fe, New Mexico; United States
